org.apache.flink.cep.nfa.compiler

类 NFACompiler.NFAFactoryCompiler<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.cep.nfa.compiler.NFACompiler.NFAFactoryCompiler<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T -
    封闭类:
    NFACompiler

    static class NFACompiler.NFAFactoryCompiler<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Converts a Pattern into graph of State. It enables sharing of compilation state across methods.

      • getCurrentNotCondition

        private java.util.List<Tuple2<IterativeCondition<T>,java.lang.String>> getCurrentNotCondition()
        Retrieves list of conditions resulting in Stop state and names of the corresponding NOT patterns.

        A current not condition can be produced in two cases:

        1. the previous pattern is a Quantifier.ConsumingStrategy#NOT_FOLLOW
        2. exists a backward path of Quantifier.QuantifierProperty#OPTIONAL patterns to Quantifier.ConsumingStrategy#NOT_FOLLOW

        WARNING: for more info on the second case see: copyWithoutTransitiveNots(State)

        返回:
        list of not conditions with corresponding names

      • copyWithoutTransitiveNots

        private State<T> copyWithoutTransitiveNots(State<T> sinkState)
        This method creates an alternative state that is target for TAKE transition from an optional State. Accepting an event in optional State discards all not Patterns that were present before it.

        E.g for a Pattern begin("a").notFollowedBy("b").followedByAny("c").optional().followedByAny("d") a sequence like : {a c b d} is a valid match, but {a b d} is not.

        NOTICE: This method creates copy only if it necessary.

        参数:
        sinkState - a state to create copy without transitive nots
        返回:
        the copy of the state itself if no modifications were needed

      • createSingletonState

        private State<T> createSingletonState(State<T> sinkState)
        Creates a simple single state. For an OPTIONAL state it also consists of a similar state without the PROCEED edge, so that for each PROCEED transition branches in computation state graph can be created only once.
        参数:
        sinkState - state that the state being converted should point to
        返回:
        the created state

      • createSingletonState

        private State<T> createSingletonState(State<T> sinkState,
                                      State<T> proceedState,
                                      IterativeCondition<T> takeCondition,
                                      IterativeCondition<T> ignoreCondition,
                                      boolean isOptional)
        Creates a simple single state. For an OPTIONAL state it also consists of a similar state without the PROCEED edge, so that for each PROCEED transition branches in computation state graph can be created only once.
        参数:
        ignoreCondition - condition that should be applied to IGNORE transition
        sinkState - state that the state being converted should point to
        proceedState - state that the state being converted should proceed to
        isOptional - whether the state being converted is optional
        返回:
        the created state

      • createLooping

        private State<T> createLooping(State<T> sinkState)
        Creates the given state as a looping one. Looping state is one with TAKE edge to itself and PROCEED edge to the sinkState. It also consists of a similar state without the PROCEED edge, so that for each PROCEED transition branches in computation state graph can be created only once.
        参数:
        sinkState - the state that the converted state should point to
        返回:
        the first state of the created complex state

      • extendWithUntilCondition

        private IterativeCondition<T> extendWithUntilCondition(IterativeCondition<T> condition,
                                                       IterativeCondition<T> untilCondition,
                                                       boolean isTakeCondition)
        This method extends the given condition with stop(until) condition if necessary. The until condition needs to be applied only if both of the given conditions are not null.
        参数:
        condition - the condition to extend
        untilCondition - the until condition to join with the given condition
        isTakeCondition - whether the condition is for TAKE edge
        返回:
        condition with AND applied or the original condition

      • getInnerIgnoreCondition

        private IterativeCondition<T> getInnerIgnoreCondition(Pattern<T,?> pattern)
        返回:
        The condition for the IGNORE edge that corresponds to the specified Pattern and extended with stop(until) condition if necessary. It is applicable only for inner states of a complex state like looping or times.
